1.content: You couldn't believe it. You just won the contest of a lifetime. You were able to spend an entire week with the WWE diva of your choice! You had so many that you wanted to choose from, buy you couldn't narrow it down. The day finally came for you to meet up with her. Who did you choose?
1.title: Contest winner.

152.content:
You were a fan of wrestling for years and had won the chance to hang out backstage on a episode of Raw and meet a bunch of the superstars and more importantly, the divas.

You even had the chance to perform in a mixed tag match. You were teamed with AJ Lee. you had seen her and she was incredibly cute, you figured if you could win you would impress her and that might help you get into her pants (or short shorts in her case)

10 minutes into the match

Your opponent had you in the ankle lock and your leg was searing with pain. somehow you managed to roll up your opponent for the three count, AJ ran to you and leapt into your arms, however your leg was in pain and you fell straight to the ground with her on top of you.

"Well this is emasculating" you thought to yourself, AJ got off you and helped you up and you headed to the back.

AJ invited you to her locker room to chat with you a bit, she immediately sat down on a bench and grabbed her ankle

"What happened" you ask
"when you fell down with me you kind of hurt my foot" she replies "would you mind giving me a foot massage" she ask

You were un sure what to do, you eventually decided
152.title: AJ lee
